snippet.title: Redshirt Trailer
snippet.description: Trailer for redshirt, the indie sci-fi life sim available from http://www.redshirtgame.com. Can you survive as a crewmember aboard the space station megalodon nine? will you learn to make friends and influence aliens? Redshirt puts you in the role of a new crew-member starting from the bottom of your career and the complex social network on-board the station. There is absolutely no need to try and leave the station and there is no truth to the rumors that the station is in danger. None whatsoever.
